About this document This document is a package vignette for the ggRandomForests package for \Visually Ex- ploring Random Forests" ( http://CRAN.R-project.org/package=ggRandomForests ).

The ggRandomForests package is designed for use with the randomForestSRC package (Ishwaran and Kogalur 2014, http://CRAN.R-project.org/package=randomForestSRC ) for growing random forests for survival (time to event response), regression (continuous response) and classication (categorical response) settings and uses the ggplot2 package (Wickham 2009, http://CRAN.R-project.org/package=ggplot2 ) for plotting diagnostic and variable associ- ation results.
